íŸ@373e02857537ca43e73f2cd58dc001c8da0bc1410f4984c2ce1934c0997beb02⁄ÀTitle: title: math avg
Path: Examples
Content:
Compute the average of a list of numbers.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> [-50 100.0 25] | math avg
25.0

```
Compute the average of a list of durations.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> [2sec 1min] | math avg
31sec

```
Compute the average of each column in a table.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> [[a b]; [1 2] [3 4]] | math avg
